{"tid":957810,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點理解irrational number","createTime":"2018-12-27T10:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T00:55:54.000Z","uid":213441,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"42b31484075cb16c0376073371932dc09a0db81e","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"假設我有一把好準嘅尺 設有1 0.1 0.01 0.001 ....... 嘅刻度 <br />\n再加一個可以無限放大嘅放大鏡方便去睇嗰啲刻度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我就畫兩條1 cm 並且互相垂直嘅線 , 再連埋佢地， 形成一個三角形 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁畢氏定理話我地知 條斜邊咪sqrt2 cm 咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我地用個放大鏡睇啲刻度嘅時候 會發現條線嘅end point 永遠喺兩個刻度之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一條線嘅長度連度都度唔到 但又真真實實存在 <br />\n真係諗到頭都爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好撚辛苦啊！！！！"},{"pid":"ec19e7a770e20cbf4ce85f96657e8000110ff21e","tid":957810,"uid":198624,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"長度呢d野係continuous value,你畫果1cm都只係大概有1cm"},{"pid":"0b1f7bae3f65ea7a38cc2781aeacabcb5293cecc","tid":957810,"uid":135445,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"你冇可能畫到真正1cm長既直線"},{"pid":"59a5381d8bdbed3afe439f24c4f766c283e4b2a1","tid":957810,"uid":147721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"如果淨係考慮1 0.1 0.01 0.001...呢堆刻度<br />\n其實0.33.....都係唔係刻度上面"},{"pid":"7c2dca941b5727460ecdbce7ed2684f94109dd2f","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04335cc37c64c72d00505246d9070141982f6dad","tid":957810,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"唔好用一個物理模型了解"},{"pid":"268cd31e60cfcb3298f2babf4fe851303678aa6e","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04335cc37c64c72d00505246d9070141982f6dad","tid":957810,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"唔好用一個物理模型了解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"why"},{"pid":"ec6aa271c7b5fced735d21a1b3343f188d3090dd","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234742a08efb94f3588edce46b78c52049bfa2c9","tid":957810,"uid":63846,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"268cd31e60cfcb3298f2babf4fe851303678aa6e","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04335cc37c64c72d00505246d9070141982f6dad","tid":957810,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"唔好用一個物理模型了解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"why"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"因為同natural number一樣只係一個人類define的mathematical construct只係你咁啱可以黎描述physical property"},{"pid":"e716e039f40c19e6931bd77b2701cf7911432647","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1462dd414d144c36a3b7ef11903d954dfe092116","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126e7257c51542124200b20ebe3e0ad5942496d7","tid":957810,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"你都識講irrational <br />\n仲想「理」解?"},{"pid":"d60fb6eaa940d4c674d87052bc85e6d898037e14","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"126e7257c51542124200b20ebe3e0ad5942496d7","tid":957810,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"你都識講irrational <br />\n仲想「理」解?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:19:16.000Z","msg":"依排係咁諗住佢 唔諗訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaf6abc379d63799c9c1d8c00cc4788e32b6983","tid":957810,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"sqrt(-1) 係宇宙暗物質，冇得解<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7136d179c287bbc9bbb6ac0560ccec73dae3d38b","tid":957810,"uid":126897,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實你講既例子關irrational number事咩?<br />\n如果我理解冇錯, 只要個長度係non-terminating decimal (e.g. 樓上所講既1/3), 咁你條線嘅end point 永遠喺兩個刻度之間架喎. <br />\n<br />\n不過正如樓上所講物理模型&quot;只係一個人類define的mathematical construct&quot;. 如果你把尺既unit係例如, sqrt2, sqrt2/10, sqrt2/100, sqrt2/1000, ... 咁你就會度到呢個長度. 姐係話如果我地定義現時我地所認知既既sqrt2 cm 為1 cm 咁你就會度到呢個長度.<br />\n<br />\n而且其實real numbers入面irrational numbers 係比rational numbers多好多好多好多好多. 現實既物理模型差唔多係冇可能完美, 你基本上係冇可能畫到真正1cm長既直線."},{"pid":"a4c487bd1f31dc0e0b9bc659c8bc27fd6fb585e4","tid":957810,"uid":208196,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"咁嘅討論係無意義<br />\nCm係人定嘅單位<br />\n如果當初果個人畫左一條線 定義為1cm<br />\n咁佢就可以畫到1cm嘅直線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁做咩無啦啦講畫唔畫到1cm嘅直線"},{"pid":"1736ad8865802d755fdf4a4bff1a9a2803a047fb","tid":957810,"uid":89046,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔睇下個definition<br />\nirrational number k 就係你搵唔到一對整數p,q 令到 k=p/q<br />\n完全唔知同尺嘅刻度有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39666f2cf7e0dc2ffaf20453ffb5da418b909da3","tid":957810,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"可以試吓搵啲physical example<br />\n例如我記得如果有兩個coupled oscillators (例如兩個鐘擺，擺喺張枱令佢哋振動互相影響)，假如兩者振動既frequency比例係rational number，喺若干時間後佢哋振動會趨於穩定，如果係irrational個oscillation就會係chaotic"},{"pid":"55a62e94f05f37336be2f82fbcebc488cc7d02be","tid":957810,"uid":58599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:25:43.000Z","msg":"正如上面個巴打講<br />\n如果把尺係將sqrt2不斷除nature number做尺<br />\n你一樣量唔到1cm出黎<br />\n咁都唔代表1係irrational"},{"pid":"2359e9f32497bb584cdd4312f5726aba85fe49f6","tid":957810,"uid":111616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"You can imagine number not only in 1 dimension"},{"pid":"7dbde6756279fa3d566688b85c171522e3b924a6","tid":957810,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"LM學野"},{"pid":"ff8d90e69565dc7283d0c6dfedca916980e0a802","tid":957810,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1736ad8865802d755fdf4a4bff1a9a2803a047fb","tid":957810,"uid":89046,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔睇下個definition<br />\nirrational number k 就係你搵唔到一對整數p,q 令到 k=p/q<br />\n完全唔知同尺嘅刻度有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"sorry 小弟柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位高手原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6e60627693138bd9e6ee5d2c08b98b7cfc6425","tid":957810,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"1/3=0.333333333...,係rational number,但永遠係刻度之間。"},{"pid":"013517173815e0e73d27741b238053c9beea2e47","tid":957810,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59a5381d8bdbed3afe439f24c4f766c283e4b2a1","tid":957810,"uid":147721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"如果淨係考慮1 0.1 0.01 0.001...呢堆刻度<br />\n其實0.33.....都係唔係刻度上面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"我諗1 0.1 0.01刻度既意思係resolution <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ninexact decimal 點都踩唔正架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36138a876316eea180ad894b5fe2c3c1da0c7182","tid":957810,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"234742a08efb94f3588edce46b78c52049bfa2c9","tid":957810,"uid":63846,"like":14,"dislike":0,"sc